SKW May Expand Through Acquisitions, Boersen-Zeitung Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-22T09:28:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-22/skw-may-expand-through-acquisitions-boersen-zeitung-reports.html
SKW Stahl-Metallurgie Holding AG (SK1) 
will continue to expand, possibly through purchases,  Boersen-
Zeitung  said, citing Chief Financial Officer Gerhard Ertl.  The “growth story of SKW is far from over,” Ertl said,
according to an article on the German newspaper’s website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  